'''2015年尼泊尔地震'''（又称'''喜马拉雅山地震'''<ref>{{cite news|author1=Cindy Tran|author2=Liam Quinn|title=Desperate families of DOZENS of Australians unaccounted in the deadly Himalayan earthquake disaster take to social media with pleas for help finding their loved ones|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3055268/If-know-pray-sister-Family-Australian-orphanage-worker-missing-huge-earthquake-rocks-Nepal-killing-700-desperate-news-loved-one.html|accessdate=2015-04-26|work=Daily Mail|date=2015-04-25|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518101242/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3055268/If-know-pray-sister-Family-Australian-orphanage-worker-missing-huge-earthquake-rocks-Nepal-killing-700-desperate-news-loved-one.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author1=Chidanand Rajghatta|title=s this the 'Big Himalayan Quake' we feared?|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Is-this-the-Big-Himalayan-Quake-we-feared/articleshow/47055477.cms|accessdate=2015-04-26|work=The Times of India|date=2015-04-26|archive-date=2015-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429005556/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Is-this-the-Big-Himalayan-Quake-we-feared/articleshow/47055477.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>）发生于[[尼泊尔标准时间|尼泊尔标准时间]]（[[UTC+5:45|UTC+5:45]]）2015年4月25日（星期六）11时56分25秒，[[震央|震央]]位於北緯28度8分49.2秒、東經84度42分28.8秒，行政區屬於[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]][[甘达基专区|甘达基专区]][[廓爾喀縣|廓爾喀縣]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/421170?tid=2 |title=《救援員把握黃金72小時‧徒手搶救生還者》，星洲日報新聞依據中國地震台網速報官方微博報導 |access-date=2015-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518095114/http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/421170?tid=2 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，約在[[拉姆琼县|拉姆琼县]]縣治[[貝西薩哈|貝西薩哈]]东南偏东34公里处，[[矩震级|矩震级]]为7.8[[矩震級|M<sub>w</sub>]]，[[面波震级|面波震级]]为8.1[[面波|M<sub>s</sub>]]，最大烈度为IX级（强烈）<ref name= USGS/>。这场地震成为继[[1934年尼泊爾-比哈爾地震|1934年地震]]后袭击该国的最强烈地震。7600多人在此次地震中丧生。受波及范围包括尼泊尔、[[印度北部|印度北部]]、[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]、[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]]、[[不丹|不丹]]和[[中國|中國]][[西藏自治区|西藏]]部分区域。本次地震还造成珠穆朗玛峰向西南偏移了3厘米<ref>{{cite news|title=尼泊尔地震致珠峰地区位移3厘米|url=http://www.cehui8.com/news/net/20150616/3109.html|accessdate=2015-12-10|publisher=中国测绘网|date=2015-06-16|archive-date=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211101631/http://www.cehui8.com/news/net/20150616/3109.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[尼泊尔标准时间|尼泊尔标准时间]]2015年5月12日12点35分，当地再次发生[[2015年5月尼泊爾地震|大地震]]，[[矩震级|矩震级]]达7.3级<ref name="Earthquake again in Nepal">{{cite web|title=Earthquake Again in Nepal 12 May 2015|url=http://naturaldisasters.tk/|website=The Natural Disasters|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505021153/http://naturaldisasters.tk/|archivedate=2015-05-05|accessdate=2015-05-15}}</ref>。震中靠近[[珠穆朗玛峰|珠穆朗玛峰]]和首都[[加德满都|加德满都]]之间的中方边境<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-32701385|title=Nepal earthquake, magnitude 7.3, strikes near Everest|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-05-12|accessdate=2015-05-15|archive-date=2015-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150515032938/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-32701385|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这一余震造成超过2500人受伤，超过125人死亡<ref name=CNN2nd>{{cite news|title=Death toll from this week's Nepal earthquake rises above 125|publisher=CNN|date=2015-05-14|author=Manesh Shrestha|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/05/14/asia/nepal-earthquake/|accessdate=2015-05-14|archive-date=2015-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150517033542/http://www.cnn.com/2015/05/14/asia/nepal-earthquake|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

