27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715041558/http://news.163.com/15/0427/07/AO6LJUVG00014Q4P.html|archive-date=2015-07-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[谷歌|谷歌]]隐私与安全团队主管在珠峰雪崩中遇难，其前明星女友在社交网络上留言与致哀。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150426/43635170_0.shtml|title=谷歌高管在珠峰雪崩中因头部重创身亡|work=凤凰网|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428055434/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150426/43635170_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://52jimo.cn/a/72d0a6f1e/2015/0426/32764.html|title=谷歌主管命丧雪崩 前明星女友悼旧爱|work=即墨市新闻网|accessdate=2015-04-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150428010017/http://52jimo.cn/a/72d0a6f1e/2015/0426/32764.html|archivedate=2015-04-28}}</ref>

尼泊尔警方出动直升机和大批军警进山救出14名伤者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/ga/2014/10-17/6690679.shtml|title=尼泊尔大雪崩致29人死亡 香港夫妇获救冻伤|work=中国新闻网|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003215100/http://www.chinanews.com/ga/2014/10-17/6690679.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。北京时间14时50分，中国女子登山队8人已乘坐直升飞机转移到了安全的地方。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://weibo.com/1726918143/Cf3NJ7Xp8?from=page_1002061726918143_profile&wvr=6&mod=weibotime&type=comment|title=王勇峰：中国女子登山队8人已转移到安全地带|work=中国青年报|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2021-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211024023610/https://weibo.com/1726918143/Cf3NJ7Xp8?from=page_1002061726918143_profile&wvr=6&mod=weibotime&type=comment}}</ref>珠峰北坡的登山者全部撤离到了安全地带，珠峰攀登活动暂时停止十天的时间。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150427/43642914_0.shtml|title=珠峰北坡登山者全撤离安全地带 攀登活动暂停十天|work=凤凰网|accessdate=2015-04-27|archive-date=2015-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526205812/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150427/43642914_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

