846/http://news.163.com/15/0427/15/AO7FJJQ700014AEE.html |archive-date=2019-01-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，山东省红十字会给予西藏灾区500床棉被<ref>{{Cite web |title=山东省红十字会向西藏地震灾区拨付500床棉被 |url=http://www.tibet.cn/news/index/xinwenfbh/201504/t20150427_2766510.htm |website=中国西藏网 |date=2015-04-27 |accessdate=2015-04-27 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115328/http://www.tibet.cn/news/index/xinwenfbh/201504/t20150427_2766510.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，浙江红十字会向西藏地震灾区提供72.5万元的救灾物资，给予灾区10万元的现金用于救灾行动<ref>{{Cite web |title=浙江红十字会向西藏地震灾区拨付82万余元赈灾款物 |url=http://news.cnfol.com/diqucaijing/20150427/20646838.shtml |website=中金在线 |date=2015-04-27 |accessdate=2015-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012142908/http://news.cnfol.com/diqucaijing/20150427/20646838.shtml |archive-date=2015-10-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，[[成都军区|成都军区]]出动9架飞机用于西藏的地震救灾行动<ref>{{Cite web |title=
